lead_paragraph: Germans appear to be tempering characteristic ambition to win the day in a Euro 2016 clash against France with higher sympathies for a core European partner hit by economic travails and militant attacks.

headline.print_headline: Soccer Mad Germans Declare Sympathy for France Before Euro Clash
